       IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
       PROGRAM-ID. CALC-INTEREST.

       DATA DIVISION.
       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
       01 WS-PRINCIPAL     PIC 9(7)V99.
       01 WS-RATE          PIC 9(3)V9999.
       01 WS-PERIODS       PIC 9(3).
       01 WS-INTEREST      PIC 9(7)V99.
       01 WS-TOTAL         PIC 9(7)V99.

       PROCEDURE DIVISION.
           ACCEPT WS-PRINCIPAL
           ACCEPT WS-RATE
           ACCEPT WS-PERIODS
           COMPUTE WS-INTEREST = WS-PRINCIPAL * WS-RATE * WS-PERIODS
           COMPUTE WS-TOTAL    = WS-PRINCIPAL + WS-INTEREST
           DISPLAY "INTEREST: " WS-INTEREST
           DISPLAY "TOTAL:    " WS-TOTAL
           STOP RUN.
